Top activities around Lille

   Lille Metropolitan Museum of Modern Art Or LaM, is located in a
   sculpture park in Villeneuve d’Ascq. According to France Voyage, it is
   the only museum in Europe to offer works of modern art, contemporary
   art and art brut. Price: around 10€, free every first Sunday of the
   month Website:…

